casebody.data:
BRISTOL-MYERS SQUIBB COMPANY
v.
S.C. (ANDERSON) S221038 Supreme Court of California August 23, 2017 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, First Appellate District, Division Two for further proceedings consistent with Bristol-Myers Squibb Co. v. Superior Court (2017) --- U.S. ----, 137 S.Ct. 1773, 198 L.Ed.2d 395.

Werdegar, J., was absent and did not participate.
